{"tid":2181424,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚晚 上乖餃子•麵","createTime":"2020-08-30T14:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T00:32:22.000Z","uid":310853,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ae68c106e2ddc28e27fedb2b2924870cf0e015ae","tid":2181424,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"今日超級慘 九半左右去咗鄰居 閘咗<br />\n極速行去 Burgerman 睇下會唔會未閘 閘埋<br />\n之後又要周圍走搵下有咩食 最後搵到依間食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLSrb3O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLSrb3O.png&h=ed74dd69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKm0gvO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKm0gvO.png&h=8bc40abe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30AsFXy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30AsFXy.png&h=dddae1d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9zEw4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9zEw4h.png&h=d1f4f797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌咗個炸醬麵 正常嘢 一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個餃子確實唔錯 咬落去係feel到有汁爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有巴打食過依間 有冇d咩麵餐攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想問下 依加長沙灣/深水埗 有咩非飯類係10點後仲會開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f142775dfd218b16ef723144d6817aa150ba48be","tid":2181424,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"似係京式炸醬麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a009c42a0e5fa4aa1e7d7c7a19e1d42e4dffd1fd","tid":2181424,"uid":61882,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"仲諗住睇吓啲餃子同麵有幾乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2953eca80b31a805a2570fb7ecb868826d02e1","tid":2181424,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f142775dfd218b16ef723144d6817aa150ba48be","tid":2181424,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"似係京式炸醬麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"類似 可能因為冇一舊舊肉所以我覺得爭少少<br />\n依間應該會有機會食多幾次其他嘢<br />\n十點後真係冇乜選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162af12a04b7c86f6ee2a71e2eba50ee052a7e39","tid":2181424,"uid":310853,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a009c42a0e5fa4aa1e7d7c7a19e1d42e4dffd1fd","tid":2181424,"uid":61882,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"仲諗住睇吓啲餃子同麵有幾乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"打錯字 太尷尬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c9ccfeef3c1efa6a4cf9eda0a949a59e9b3048","tid":2181424,"uid":146203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"羊肉餃子唔錯"},{"pid":"673a6cd038c315d5205718d3c8e7c035a627a0e2","tid":2181424,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25c9ccfeef3c1efa6a4cf9eda0a949a59e9b3048","tid":2181424,"uid":146203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"羊肉餃子唔錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"Yes 我食羊 巴打係咪有食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇咩麵係好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c021cb96c425e420fb39da7e92916abd9568a2","tid":2181424,"uid":146203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"673a6cd038c315d5205718d3c8e7c035a627a0e2","tid":2181424,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"